name: Console Hack Typer
description:
CONSOLE SIMULATOR!

In this game, you can hack things. But it's not real, for the fun or prank. Game have specialcommands(DDOS, Virus, Firewall..).
Also you can write what you want! Commands are not required!

FEATURES:

-Special Commands
-Custom Code(You can write what you want)
-Choosing a Target IP or ID
-Choosing a Name

UPCOMING UPDATES:

-More Commands
